    "body": "No, this is reproduced in Windows Terminal.\r\n\r\n`%LOCALAPPDATA%\\Packages\\Microsoft.WindowsTerminal_8wekyb3d8bbwe\\LocalState\\settings.json` snippet\r\n\r\n```json\r\n\"profiles\": {\r\n    \"list\": [\r\n        {\r\n                \"commandline\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\XXXXXXXX\\\\.local\\\\bin\\\\xonsh.exe\",\r\n                \"guid\": \"{b7af3958-5b9a-4e3f-ad60-de1f84338908}\",\r\n                \"hidden\": false,\r\n                \"icon\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\XXXXXXXX\\\\Pictures\\\\conch_pixel-128.png\",\r\n                \"name\": \"xonsh\",\r\n                \"startingDirectory\": null\r\n         }\r\n    ]\r\n}\r\n```",
