    "updated_at": "2024-02-21T15:52:50Z",
    "body": "There is a manual fix, run `starship init --print-full-init xonsh` and copy/paste the output into `~/.xonshrc`, modify paths to xonsh as appropriate. I just replaced it with `xonsh` as `%USERPROFILE%/.local/bin` is on my PATH.",
